---
title: Creamy Coconut Fish Curry with Yukon Potatoes, Sweet Peas, and Cilantro
description: Inspired by the coastal Malabar region of India, this pungent yellow curry is mellowed by velvety coconut milk. Cooking the potatoes in the coconut broth helps thicken the sauce, while infusing the potatoes with intense flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5654b0904dab71da508b4568.jpg
